* Automate Retention with\nPredictive Optimization
** What it automates
***_ VACUUM (remove unreferenced files)
***_ OPTIMIZE (file layout)
***_ ANALYZE (update statistics)
** Enable
***_ ALTER SCHEMA ... ENABLE PREDICTIVE OPTIMIZATION
***_ Enabled by default (accounts after Nov 2024)
** Set retention first
***_ Set deletedFileRetentionDuration before enabling
***_ Default VACUUM = 7 days
** Monitor
***_ system.storage.predictive_optimization_operations_history
***_ Operations, timing, costs
@endmindmap
